    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E46 M3, representing the zenith of BMW M\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS for instantaneous throttle response. This example is mechanically peerless: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. Power is transmitted via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematic integrity with no bushing deflection or oxidation. Finished in pristine Carbon Black, this vehicle offers a pure, tactile driving experience for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
