    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its factory luster without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or blemish. Every body panel is original, and the wheels are free of any curb rash or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is firm and shows no signs of wear or creasing, while the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the dual-zone climate control, operate with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by brand-certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and clean, reflecting the mechanical integrity of the vehicle. This sale includes the full set of original keys, all owner's manuals, and a documented history folder. For the buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor, this is the definitive choice.",
